      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R2 used under ISO 9001-certified QMS; documented software validation plan and test suite executed prior to each analysis campaign.",
      "rationale": "The FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical 2023 R2) is deployed under a DePuy Synthes ISO 9001-certified quality management system. Software validation records confirm execution of the vendor-supplied verification suite with zero critical failures. Change-control procedures prevent unauthorized solver updates between analysis runs. Required Gradation 2 is satisfied."
