      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities replicate the COU loading mode, device geometry, and regulatory test standard (ASTM F1717) with no material deviations.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity directly replicates the COU: same device design (non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw), same loading mode (static compression-bending), same regulatory standard (ASTM F1717), and same QoIs. Testing was performed at two independent laboratories to assess inter-laboratory reproducibility. No material deviations between validation scenario and COU were identified. Required Gradation 2 is satisfied."
