    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 1 vs. required Gradation 2) is accepted based on the supporting computational sensitivity analysis demonstrating low sensitivity of QoIs to screw spacing and rod diameter variations within the design space. All three QoIs satisfy both the < 10% percent difference and E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criteria. The model is accepted for use in the declared COU.",
